ontologyFramework.OFDataMapping.ReservatedDataType

Class Procedure

  • java.lang.Object
    • ontologyFramework.OFDataMapping.ReservatedDataType.Procedure

  • public class Procedure
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the default procedure mapping used from this framework. This requires that default procedure mast be represented in this way, other procedures may use customizable mappers. To allow so, this class should implement the java object to use to address to a procedure.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Buoncomapgni Luca

      • Procedure

        public Procedure(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual scheduler,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual event,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual timeTrigger,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual synchronization,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLLiteral procedureName,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLLiteral concurrrentPoolSize,
         org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLLiteral checkerFreqInMillisec)
        Create a new procedure object initialize with some needed quantities.
        Parameters:
        scheduler - which address to the individual that describe a scheduler in the ontology
        event - top abstraction individual that represent the event for this procedure. It will run only at timeTriggrt time & if its event result true at checking time.
        timeTrigger - ontological individual that represents the quartz object to define the next trigger for this procedure.
        synchronization - individual that represents if this procedure should run only when other procedures have done their work.
        procedureName - which represent a string with the fully qualifier to the implementation of the procedure.
        concurrrentPoolSize - which represents an Integer for the size of the quartz scheduler pool.
        checkerFreqInMillisec - which represents a Long to describe the frequency too check the state of the events assign to this object.

        public static Procedure getSimpleCleaner(OWLReferences ontoRef)
        Static methods which returns a simple Procedure object. It will be initialized with respect to the following individual: 
         
 new Procedure(
			 OWLLibrary.getOWLIndividual( "Sc_Scheduler1", ontoRef), 
			 OWLLibrary.getOWLIndividual( "Ev_CleanerEvent", ontoRef),
			 null,
			 OWLLibrary.getOWLIndividual( "P_ReasonerUpdater", ontoRef),
			 OWLLibrary.getOWLLiteral( "ontologyFramework.OFProcedureManagment.OFProcedureImplementation.Cleaner", ontoRef),
	 		 OWLLibrary.getOWLLiteral( 1L, ontoRef),
			 OWLLibrary.getOWLLiteral( 100000L, ontoRef))
        Parameters:
        ontoRef - reference to an OWLOntology
        Returns:
        a simple reasoner updating procedure.
